	(4,'Great Expectations','2013-09-11-great-expectations','2013-09-11 14:48:00','For those who are unfamiliar with Dickens’s brilliant insight into pre-Victorian England, Great Expectations begins with an orphaned boy’s terrifying encounter with an escaped convict. It sets in motion dramatic changes in his life. Later, he turns his back on his humble beginnings as a blacksmith’s apprentice and strives to better himself as a London gentleman. He is also in hot pursuit of the love of his childhood, the cold but stunningly beautiful, Estella. Through it all, he is blissfully unaware of the dangers awaiting him.\r\n\r\nThe story has deep resonances for all young people even today as it brings the hopes and dreams of youth into the complex realities of adulthood.\r\n\r\nIt is anticipated that the season of Great Expectations will fill up fast so it is highly advisable to book early by phoning 430 4460 as soon as possible. Tickets cost $14, $10 for senior citizens and just $8 for students.\r\n\r\nh2. Great Expectations season:\r\n* Tuesday, September 17th  7.00pm.  Special $6 Preview\r\n* Wednesday, September 18th Opening Night\r\n\r\nDinner and show also available!\r\n\r\nThen:\r\n\r\n* Thursday, 19th September – Saturday 21st September\r\n\r\nAll shows start at 7.00pm\r\n\r\nDon’t miss it!','<p>For those who are unfamiliar with Dickens’s brilliant insight into pre-Victorian England, Great Expectations begins with an orphaned boy’s terrifying encounter with an escaped convict. It sets in motion dramatic changes in his life. Later, he turns his back on his humble beginnings as a blacksmith’s apprentice and strives to better himself as a London gentleman. He is also in hot pursuit of the love of his childhood, the cold but stunningly beautiful, Estella. Through it all, he is blissfully unaware of the dangers awaiting him.</p>\n\n<p>The story has deep resonances for all young people even today as it brings the hopes and dreams of youth into the complex realities of adulthood