	(127,48,232,8,1,1000,'{\"_id\":\"48\",\"intro_text\":\"With Whangarei being only a 20 minute flight from Auckland city, and the doorway to the rest of Northland, it is no wonder that many visitors and students flock to this city to enjoy the best of both worlds.\",\"_title\":\"With Whangarei being only a 20 minute flight from Auckland city, and the doorway to the rest of Northland, it is no wonder that many visitors and students flock to this city to enjoy the best of both worlds.\"}',' With Whangarei being only a 20 minute flight from Auckland city, and the doorway to the rest of Northland, it is no wonder that many visitors and students flock to this city to enjoy the best of both worlds. '),
