	(140,54,46,23,1,1000,'{\"_id\":\"54\",\"text\":{\"raw\":\"WGHS is highly regarded for its attractive physical setting and well-resourced classrooms, particularly its: purpose-built (specialist) classrooms, hospitality suite (opened in 2006),impressive library(opened in 2000) and well-equipped science & technology suites. Enhancing student learning in an attractive environment is a key advantage at WGHS.\\r\\n\\r\\n- 6 computer labs, most with high power capability for design programmes.\\r\\n- A space dedicated to International Students.\\r\\n- Music Suite\\r\\n- Well equipped Fideliter Centre with three gymnasiums including the brand new Manawahine Gym with it\'s full size netball court.\\r\\n- An all weather playing surface, climbing wall, swimming pool with diving boards, tennis courts.\\r\\n- A large modern technology block.\\r\\n- A modern well resourced Library.\\r\\n\\r\\nA Performing Arts Centre for Drama and Dance is now in the planning stages and aiming to be ready for use beginning of 2012. This will enhance our already strong reputation for excellence in the Performing Arts.\",\"processed\":\"<p>WGHS is highly regarded for its attractive physical setting and well-resourced classrooms, particularly its: purpose-built (specialist) classrooms, hospitality suite (opened in 2006),impressive library(opened in 2000) and well-equipped science & technology suites. Enhancing student learning in an attractive environment is a key advantage at WGHS.<\\/p>\\n\\n<ul>\\n<li>6 computer labs, most with high power capability for design programmes.<\\/li>\\n<li>A space dedicated to International Students.<\\/li>\\n<li>Music Suite<\\/li>\\n<li>Well equipped Fideliter Centre with three gymnasiums including the brand new Manawahine Gym with it\\u2019s full size netball court.<\\/li>\\n<li>An all weather playing surface, climbing wall, swimming pool with diving boards, tennis courts.<\\/li>\\n<li>A large modern technology block.<\\/li>\\n<li>A modern well resourced Library.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n\\n<p>A Performing Arts Centre for Drama and Dance is now in the planning stages and aiming to be ready for use beginning of 2012. This will enhance our already strong reputation for excellence in the Performing Arts.<\\/p>\\n\"}}',' WGHS is highly regarded for its attractive physical setting and well-resourced classrooms, particularly its: purpose-built (specialist) classrooms, hospitality suite (opened in 2006),impressive library(opened in 2000) and well-equipped science & technology suites. Enhancing student learning in an attractive environment is a key advantage at WGHS.\n\n\n6 computer labs, most with high power capability for design programmes.\nA space dedicated to International Students.\nMusic Suite\nWell equipped Fideliter Centre with three gymnasiums including the brand new Manawahine Gym with it’s full size netball court.\nAn all weather playing surface, climbing wall, swimming pool with diving boards, tennis courts.\nA large modern technology block.\nA modern well resourced Library.\n\n\nA Performing Arts Centre for Drama and Dance is now in the planning stages and aiming to be ready for use beginning of 2012. This will enhance our already strong reputation for excellence in the Performing Arts.\n '),
