	(145,56,12,6,2,1000,'{\"_id\":\"56\",\"text\":{\"raw\":\"Whangarei Girls\' High School is the only girls\' school north of Auckland and the only one with a boarding hostel, which provides accomodation for students from Northland and overseas.\\r\\n\\r\\nOur staff favourites\\r\\n--------------------\\r\\n\\r\\n- Member One: [\\\"There is nothing better than a game of golf at Denby\\\"](http:\\/\\/www.nzgolfcourses.co.nz\\/whangarei\\/ \\\"Denby Golf Course\\\")\\r\\n- Member Two: [\\\"I love the coffee at Caffeine\\\"](http:\\/\\/www.caffeinecafe.co.nz\\/ \\\"Caffeine Cafe Whangarei\\\")\\r\\n\\r\\nFind our students in the weekend\\r\\n--------------------------------\\r\\n- Student one: [\\\"I beat all my friends at tenpin bowling\\\"](http:\\/\\/www.10pin.co.nz\\/ \\\"Whangarei Tenpin Bowling\\\")\\r\\n- Student two: [\\\"Swimming at Ocean Beach is the best thing on a summers day\\\"](http:\\/\\/www.findabeach.co.nz\\/beaches\\/ocean-beach-whangarei\\/about\\/ \\\"Ocean Beach Whangarei\\\")\\r\\n- Student three: [\\\"A work out at the gym after school is great relax\\\"](http:\\/\\/anytimefitnesswhangarei.co.nz\\/ \\\"\\\")\\r\\n\\r\\nOther interesting links\\r\\n-----------------------\\r\\n\\r\\n- [Whangarei on WikiVoyage](http:\\/\\/en.wikivoyage.org\\/wiki\\/Whangarei \\\"\\\")\\r\\n- [Tourism Northland](http:\\/\\/www.northlandnz.com\\/ \\\"\\\")\\r\\n- [This is the place](http:\\/\\/thisistheplace.org.nz\\/ \\\"\\\")\",\"processed\":\"<p>Whangarei Girls\\u2019 High School is the only girls\\u2019 school north of Auckland and the only one with a boarding hostel, which provides accomodation for students from Northland and overseas.<\\/p>\\n\\n<h2>Our staff favourites<\\/h2>\\n\\n<ul>\\n<li>Member One: <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.nzgolfcourses.co.nz\\/whangarei\\/\\\" title=\\\"Denby Golf Course\\\">\\u201cThere is nothing better than a game of golf at Denby\\u201d<\\/a><\\/li>\\n<li>Member Two: <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.caffeinecafe.co.nz\\/\\\" title=\\\"Caffeine Cafe Whangarei\\\">\\u201cI love the coffee at Caffeine\\u201d<\\/a><\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n\\n<h2>Find our students in the weekend<\\/h2>\\n\\n<ul>\\n<li>Student one: <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.10pin.co.nz\\/\\\" title=\\\"Whangarei Tenpin Bowling\\\">\\u201cI beat all my friends at tenpin bowling\\u201d<\\/a><\\/li>\\n<li>Student two: <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.findabeach.co.nz\\/beaches\\/ocean-beach-whangarei\\/about\\/\\\" title=\\\"Ocean Beach Whangarei\\\">\\u201cSwimming at Ocean Beach is the best thing on a summers day\\u201d<\\/a><\\/li>\\n<li>Student three: <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/anytimefitnesswhangarei.co.nz\\/\\\" title=\\\"\\\">\\u201cA work out at the gym after school is great relax\\u201d<\\/a><\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n\\n<h2>Other interesting links<\\/h2>\\n\\n<ul>\\n<li><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/en.wikivoyage.org\\/wiki\\/Whangarei\\\" title=\\\"\\\">Whangarei on WikiVoyage<\\/a><\\/li>\\n<li><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.northlandnz.com\\/\\\" title=\\\"\\\">Tourism Northland<\\/a><\\/li>\\n<li><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/thisistheplace.org.nz\\/\\\" title=\\\"\\\">This is the place<\\/a><\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n\"}}',' Whangarei Girls’ High School is the only girls’ school north of Auckland and the only one with a boarding hostel, which provides accomodation for students from Northland and overseas.\n\nOur staff favourites\n\n\nMember One: “There is nothing better than a game of golf at Denby”\nMember Two: “I love the coffee at Caffeine”\n\n\nFind our students in the weekend\n\n\nStudent one: “I beat all my friends at tenpin bowling”\nStudent two: “Swimming at Ocean Beach is the best thing on a summers day”\nStudent three: “A work out at the gym after school is great relax”\n\n\nOther interesting links\n\n\nWhangarei on WikiVoyage\nTourism Northland\nThis is the place\n\n '),
