	(12,6,'Content','/about-wghs/location/index.php','<p>Whangarei Girls’ High School is the only girls’ school north of Auckland and the only one with a boarding hostel, which provides accomodation for students from Northland and overseas.</p>\n\n<h2>Our staff favourites</h2>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Member One: <a href=\"http://www.nzgolfcourses.co.nz/whangarei/\" title=\"Denby Golf Course\">“There is nothing better than a game of golf at Denby”</a></li>\n<li>Member Two: <a href=\"http://www.caffeinecafe.co.nz/\" title=\"Caffeine Cafe Whangarei\">“I love the coffee at Caffeine”</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Find our students in the weekend</h2>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Student one: <a href=\"http://www.10pin.co.nz/\" title=\"Whangarei Tenpin Bowling\">“I beat all my friends at tenpin bowling”</a></li>\n<li>Student two: <a href=\"http://www.findabeach.co.nz/beaches/ocean-beach-whangarei/about/\" title=\"Ocean Beach Whangarei\">“Swimming at Ocean Beach is the best thing on a summers day”</a></li>\n<li>Student three: <a href=\"http://anytimefitnesswhangarei.co.nz/\" title=\"\">“A work out at the gym after school is great relax”</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Other interesting links</h2>\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/Whangarei\" title=\"\">Whangarei on WikiVoyage</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.northlandnz.com/\" title=\"\">Tourism Northland</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://thisistheplace.org.nz/\" title=\"\">This is the place</a></li>\n</ul>\n',0,2,'text_block.html',0,'{\"edit_mode\":\"singlepage\"}',1,2,2,'*'),
