	(58,29,'Content','/about-wghs/sponsor-wghs.php','<h2>Slingshot ‘Better Schools’ Programme</h2>\n\n<p>We are now part of this wonderful programme whereby Slingshot customers can choose to have a percentage of their monthly bill donated to the school. Each month, Slingshot will send us a cheque to use as we see fit. How big that cheque is depends on you! If you’d like this easy and pain free way to contribute please go to <a href=\"http://www.slingshot.co.nz/schools\" title=\"\">www.slingshot.co.nz/schools</a> or call 0800 89 2000 and speak to one of their friendly customer helpers.</p>\n\n<h3>Who is Slingshot?</h3>\n\n<p>Slingshot is New Zealand’s largest 100% kiwi owned phone and internet company. They focus on keeping things simple, and providing better service and better value than the big guys.</p>\n',0,3,'text_block.html',0,'{\"edit_mode\":\"singlepage\"}',1,1,1,'*'),
	(62,31,'Content','/about-wghs/board-of-trustees.php','<h2>Board of Trustees Members</h2>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Sue Cresswell - Chairperson</li>\n<li>George Beasley - Deputy Chairperson</li>\n<li>Laura Baker</li>\n<li>Anne Cooper - Principal</li>\n<li>Melissa Gilbert</li>\n<li>Wendy Rees - Staff Representative\nB- ridget Westenra</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Board of Trustee meetings for 2014:</h2>\n\n<ul>\n<li>March 17</li>\n<li>May 26</li>\n<li>June 23</li>\n<li>July 28</li>\n<li>August 25</li>\n<li>September 22</li>\n<li>October 28</li>\n<li>November 24</li>\n<li>December - date to be confirmed</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>All meetings held at 5.30pm in either the WGHS staffroom or Hall Theatre Foyer.</p>\n',0,2,'text_block.html',0,'{\"edit_mode\":\"singlepage\"}',1,1,1,'*'),
	(347,35,'Intro text','/news-events/index.php','\n<p class=\"intro-text\">In this section you will find the latest news and events involving Whangarei Girls\' High School, along with our event calendar and school newsletters.</p>\n<hr />\n',0,1,'_intro_text.html',0,'{\"searchURL\":\"\",\"title_delimit\":\"\",\"adminOnly\":0,\"addToTop\":0,\"limit\":false,\"edit_mode\":\"listdetail\"}',1,3,3,'*'),
