	(1,'Waitangi Day','2014-02-06-waitangi-day','2014-02-06 00:00:00','School closed.','<p>School closed.</p>','[]'),
	(2,'Test event','2014-02-17-test-event','2014-02-17 23:52:00','Lorem ipsum','<p>Lorem ipsum</p>','[]'),
	(3,'Parent Interviews #1','2014-04-03-parent-interviews-1','2014-04-03 14:30:00','2.30pm - 4.45pm.\r\n\r\nThis year we are again using online interview bookings which were so successfully trailled last year. Hopefully this will make it easier for you to make a time to meet with teachers to discuss your daughter\'s start to the 2014 academic year. Interviews take place on the afternoons of Thursday 3 April and Wednesday 9 April starting at 2.30pm and ending at 4.45pm. School progress reports will be issued on Friday 28 March.\r\n\r\nBookings will go live from Friday 28 March.\r\n\r\n\"Online Booking\":/perch/resources/parent-letter-2014-online-booking.docx Click here for Online Booking information','<p>2.30pm &#8211; 4.45pm.</p>\n\n<p>This year we are again using online interview bookings which were so successfully trailled last year. Hopefully this will make it easier for you to make a time to meet with teachers to discuss your daughter&#8217;s start to the 2014 academic year. Interviews take place on the afternoons of Thursday 3 April and Wednesday 9 April starting at 2.30pm and ending at 4.45pm. School progress reports will be issued on Friday 28 March.</p>\n\n<p>Bookings will go live from Friday 28 March.</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"/perch/resources/parent-letter-2014-online-booking.docx\">Online Booking</a> Click here for Online Booking information</p>','[]'),
	(4,'NZSS Adventure Racing Champs','2014-04-04-nzss-adventure-racing-champs','2014-04-04 08:00:00','4 April 2014 to 06 April 2014','<p>4 April 2014 to 06 April 2014</p>','[]'),
