	(7,'NSSSA Beach Volleyball','2014-04-10-nsssa-beach-volleyball','2014-04-10 09:00:00','NSSSA Beach Volleyball','<p><span class=\"caps\">NSSSA</span> Beach Volleyball</p>','[]'),
	(8,'Early Finish for Students 12.15PM','2014-04-10-early-finish-for-students-1215pm','2014-04-10 12:15:00','Paid Union Meeting for the Post Primary Teachers Association (PPTA) on Thursday 10 April.\r\n\r\nClasses will run as normal for the first three periods, but there will be no classes after 12.15pm.\r\n\r\nBuses will run at the scheduled times.','<p>Paid Union Meeting for the Post Primary Teachers Association (<span class=\"caps\">PPTA</span>) on Thursday 10 April.</p>\n\n<p>Classes will run as normal for the first three periods, but there will be no classes after 12.15pm.</p>\n\n<p>Buses will run at the scheduled times.</p>','[]'),
